perfcenter.baseclass

Class QueuingResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • perfcenter.baseclass.QueuingResource
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Device, SoftServer, VirtualResource

    public abstract class QueuingResource
extends java.lang.Object
    This class abstracts the queuing resources like Device, LanLink and SoftServer. Many of the methods and functionality is similar across these classes, and this abstraction was created to reduce the code redundancy in the project.
